1) Empty Credentials Test
Step definition:
- Navigate to «Welcome to Puppy Bank» page
- Leave the «Username» field empty
- Leave the «Password» field empty
- Click «Log in» button
Expected result:
- Browser errors about unfilled fields exist.
- The browser error message contains correct text.
- User stays on the "Welcome to Puppy Bank" page

2) Empty Username Field Test
Step definition:
- Navigate to «Welcome to Puppy Bank» page
- Leave the «Username» field empty
-Enter "password" in the "Password" field
- Click «Log in» button
Expected result:
- Browser errors about unfilled fields exist.
- The browser error message contains correct text.
- User stays on the "Welcome to Puppy Bank" page

3) Empty Password Field Test
Step definition:
- Navigate to «Welcome to Puppy Bank» page
- Enter "admin" in the "Username" field
- Leave the «Password» field empty
- Click «Log in» button
Expected result:
- Browser errors about unfilled fields exist.
- The browser error message contains correct text.
- User stays on the "Welcome to Puppy Bank" page